Interface DataFetcher.DataCallback<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of data that will be loaded.
    Enclosing interface:
    DataFetcher<T>

    public static interface DataFetcher.DataCallback<T>
    Callback that should be called when data has been loaded and is available, or when the load fails.
